  <Heading3
    title="2. Marketing UI & Conversion Flow"
    subtitle="With the design system in place, I designed the top-of-funnel web experience. The goal here was not just visual appeal, but conversion architecture—crafting clear messaging, intuitive navigation, and strategic calls-to-action designed to funnel visitors smoothly into the application's onboarding flow."
